data.eml:eml: A new genus and species of Sieblosiidae from the Middle Miocene of Germany (Odonata: Epiproctophora)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Nel, André, Fleck, Gunther (2012): A new genus and species of Sieblosiidae from the Middle Miocene of Germany (Odonata: Epiproctophora). Zootaxa 3582: 64-68, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.283081
